casebody.data:
LH WAGNER REALTY CORPORATION and Leo H. Wagner, Plaintiffs-Movants,
v.
Bob MARTIN, Commissioner, New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection, Defendant. M-1003/1004 September Term 2018
082062 Supreme Court of New Jersey. JUNE 3, 2019

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motions for leave to file a motion for reconsideration as within time (M-1003) and for reconsideration of the Court's order denying the petition for certification (M-1004) are denied.
